    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时间是一笔财富，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你回到那个夏天，你想的是：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这两个月的暑假里，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如何去挥霍它！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演“王一点”，清晨从家里出发，穿梭在故乡的小城里，享受自由自在的时光，在夕阳落下时尽兴而归。日复一日，你可以：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以 3D 平台跳跃的形式探索城市的每个角落；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与形形色色的人物交谈互动；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >捕捉各种稀奇古怪的昆虫和生物；</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264420/extras/c8fd96304833f17fefd3733ec5b6f575.poster.avif?t=1765331212\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264420/extras/c8fd96304833f17fefd3733ec5b6f575.webm?t=1765331212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264420/extras/c8fd96304833f17fefd3733ec5b6f575.mp4?t=1765331212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过各种活动提高自身的身体数值；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游走于现实与非现实世界间；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解决各种谜题；</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264420/extras/ef9713afba568fffa559f9bb96a2dab2.poster.avif?t=1765331212\" width=612 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264420/extras/ef9713afba568fffa559f9bb96a2dab2.webm?t=1765331212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264420/extras/ef9713afba568fffa559f9bb96a2dab2.mp4?t=1765331212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有：这是个开放式的 RPG 游戏，含有多个结局。</p>",
